name: Brazilian Bundles
description:
Brazilian Hair:

The quality of this hair is Soft, Silky and Smooth and can be treated as if it is your own hair, it
can be washed, cut, straightened, dyed, shampooed, conditioned, blow dryed, moisturized, curled
and styled as desired to create a completely undetectable, natural, comfortable and stylish look
within minutes. The hair is soft with a natural shine to it. With good maintenance, the hair can be
used several times over and over again, lasting up to 1 year!

name: Burmese Bundles
description: Burmese hair is not too widely known but its is gorgeous and a favorite of many that do know it. Burmese hair is cross between Chinese and Indian hair. It is healthy, resilient and full bodied. It is naturally straight with a slight curl at the end. Burmese hair is well suited for people of African decent and those that like naturally straight hair.

name: Peruvian Bundles
description: Virgin Peruvian hair is one of the most exotic hair types in the market. Virgin Peruvian hair has many purpose, it is lightweight but still carries lots of volume. It has soft and silky texture, available in natural black. As usual, we only offer 100% Virgin Hair, therefore our Peruvian hair is obtained from a single donor and has not been chemically altered or processed. It is Shed-Free and Tangle-Free, so you can rest assured that you are purchasing top notch hair.

name: Cambodian Double Bundles
description: This virgin Cambodian hair features soft waves, a smooth and silky texture, and adds a bit of Hollywood glamour to any style. Our Cambodian hair has a high, sleek gloss with a super soft touch.

name: Filipino Double Bundles
description: Our Filipino hair is perfect for anyone looking for bombshell body and volume! This hair is extremely bouncy and will sway with every step you take. Our incredibly gorgeous Filipino hair, has a medium to low luster. It will blend effortlessly with relaxed, or pressed natural hair. Love curling your hair? No problem this hair holds curls beautifully so no worries about them falling! Like to color? That's perfectly fine! This hair will take dye, and bleach extremely well due to its Virgin Nature.

name: Peruvian Double Bundles
description: Virgin Peruvian hair is one of the most exotic hair types in the market. Virgin Peruvian hair has many purpose, it is lightweight but still carries lots of volume. It has soft and silky texture, available in natural black. As usual, we only offer 100% Virgin Hair, therefore our Peruvian hair is obtained from a single donor and has not been chemically altered or processed. It is Shed-Free and Tangle-Free, so you can rest assured that you are purchasing top notch hair.

name: Russian Blonde Double Bundles
description: Russian Blonde Virgin Hair is the most exclusive beautiful and rare type of hair which is why is cost more then the other types of virgin hair. Russian Blonde Hair is the purest and silkiest of all the virgin hair. The hair is of Russian Descent it is the finest of all virgin hair on the market. Our Russian Blonde Virgin Hair comes in a light blonde to a medium Blonde. The hair tend not to go darker than brown. The hair is extremely versatile and can be straightened as well as curled.

name: Brazilian & Peruvian Silk Base Closure
description:
Our Silk Base Lace Closures are truly undetectable and gives off the illusion as if the hair was coming directly from your scalp.

We offer the best rate on the market and our closures are made at a natural length.

Our closures are measured at a perfect size and has a natural scalp appearance. All closures comes in length of 16 and natural color, which is normally 1b or #2 (off black color- dark brown). All of our closures are made with 100% Virgin Human Hair. It can also be colored, please consult with your stylist.

The measurement of our closures are the perfect size of 3.5 X 3. These closures can be worn over and over. They can last up to 1 year with proper care.

name: Brazilian & Peruvian Swiss Lace Closure

name: 13x4 Frontal Lace Closures-Brazilian
description:
